    Class
    Description
    Attacking
    Represents an abstract class for attacking plants in a game.
    Board
    Represents the game board in a tower-defense style game such as Plants vs.
    Cell
    Represents a single cell in a game grid.
    Character
    Represents a character in a game with basic functionality such as health management.
    Defensive
    The Defensive class is an abstract subclass of Plant that serves as a blueprint for creating defensive plant types in a game.
    GameManager
    The GameManager class is responsible for managing the game's state, resources, and interactions in the Player vs Player mode.
    GameManagerPvsMO
    GameManagerPvsMO is responsible for managing the game's core functionality in the Player vs Machine (ZombiesOriginal) mode.
    Generate
    The Generate class is an abstract subclass of Zombies, designed for entities that possess the ability to generate "brains" as resources in the game.
    Movement
    Represents a zombie with movement capabilities in the game.
    Plant
    Represents a plant in a game, such as a strategy or tower defense game, that inherits from the Character class.
    POOBvsZOMBIESException
    Represents custom exceptions specific to the POOBvsZOMBIES game.
    Support
    The Support class is an abstract extension of the Plant class, designed to represent a type of plant in the game that generates sunlight at regular intervals.
    Zombies
    Represents an abstract Zombie entity within the game.
